ut-us.aspx\">The Church of England</a>\r\n\t        </li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    \t<li class=\"column-2 \">\r\n\t            <a href=\"http://www.secularism.org.uk/\">National Secular Society</a>\r\n\t        </li>\r\n\t\t    </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n  \t\t\r\n<div class=\"related-bbc-links\">\r\n\t<h3>Around the BBC</h3>\r\n\t<ul class=\"related-links\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    \t<li class=\"column-1  first-child\">\r\n\t            <a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/religion/religions/atheism/history/secularism.shtml\">BBC Religion: Morality and secularism</a>\r\n\t        </li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    \t<li class=\"column-1 \">\r\n\t            <a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yktfc\">BBC Radio 4: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke - Church and state</a>\r\n\t        </li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    \t<li class=\"column-2 \">\r\n\t            <a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b01g5znw\">BBC Radio 4: Beyond Belief - Monarchy</a>\r\n\t        </li>\r\n\t\t    </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n        <p class=\"disclaimer\">The BBC is not responsible for the content of external Internet sites</p>\r\n\t</div>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">$render(\"page-related-items\",\"ID\");</script>\r\n\n  </div>\n\n      \n  <div class=\"share-body-bottom\">\n\t<div id=\"page-bookmark-links-foot\" class=\"share-help\">\r\n  <h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n  <ul>  \t\r\n    <li class=\"delicious\">\r\n      <a title=\"Post this story to Delicious\" href=\"http://del.icio.us/post?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/religion/0/21883918&amp;title=BBC+Religion+%26+Ethics+-+Perspectives%3A+Should+Britain+become+a+secular+state%3F\">Delicious</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"digg\">\r\n      <a title=\"Post this story to Digg\" href=\"http://digg.com/submit?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/religion/0/21883918&amp;title=BBC+Religion+%26+Ethics+-+Perspectives%3A+Should+Britain+become+a+secular+state%3F\">Digg</a